{"tid":1559029,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會需要正視聽 ，政府對旅遊業困局了無作為，甚至今日困局係政府一手造成","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:58:14.000Z","uid":71606,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05d754dc95bc23782e5750497a66cac1557a7f5b","tid":1559029,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"前排旅遊業同埋政府沖曬出嚟 ，同大家講示威搞到冇旅客<br />\n生意慘淡乜乜<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>參考資料 陳茂波稱上月訪港旅客持續下跌 比去年同期減近4成<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479466-20190908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479466-20190908.htm&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=d503aa1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479466-20190908.htm&h=d50dc992\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479466-20190908.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我突然間又諗返起一單新聞㗎喎<br />\n我哋鄰近友好地區 台灣<br />\n因為大選將近嘅關係<br />\n亦都畀強國制裁<br />\n唔畀自由行到訪<br />\n同樣面臨冇曬大陸客嘅困境<br />\n咁呢一刻嘅佢哋又做緊啲咩呢<br />\n係咪走去同蔡英文講話佢搞亂曬成個社會呢<br />\n於是我又做咗少少資料搜習<br />\n<blockquote>參考資料  老外打臉習維尼！外國人看中國禁止來台自由行｜《老外不議外》 EP.8<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oyf8LVgdI5U&amp;t=191s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Doyf8LVgdI5U%26t%3D191s&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=1993fb50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oyf8LVgdI5U&amp;t=191s</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯喺缺少大陸旅客嘅情況底下，所有外國嘅旅客人數反而上升<br />\n咁究竟當中發生咗咩事呢<br />\n台灣政府面臨困局嘅時候有啲咩做過呢<br />\n我哋再睇多少少<br />\n<blockquote>參考資料  郵輪年帶上萬旅客來台 採購破億元商機<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190831/32511976.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190831%2F32511976.html&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=de6bdf08\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190831/32511976.html</a><br />\n中央社 (2019-08-31 14:41)<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先第一點佢哋大力發展郵輪旅遊，仲有唔錯嘅成效<br />\n我哋香港好彩都唔輸蝕，有一個「睇得」郵輪碼頭<br />\n冇錯真係淨係睇下<br />\n因為根本冇咩人去，亦都冇咩旅客<br />\n<blockquote>參考資料  議員轟啟德郵輪碼頭如死城 政府死撐人流達預期<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190109/bkn-20190109122309529-0109_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190109%2Fbkn-20190109122309529-0109_00822_001.html&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=755ac459\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190109/bkn-20190109122309529-0109_00822_001.html</a><br />\n2019年01月09日(三) 12:23<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之後係第二點台灣開始發展醫療旅遊<br />\n香港呢你有咩競爭力有咩賣點<br />\n或者咁講香港政府你做過啲咩嘢令到香港有賣點<br />\n用幾十萬買一個廣告話自己好客城市<br />\n做開服務業嘅人都知道，呢一行到底有幾好客<br />\n而且退多一萬步講，好客都唔係一個賣點<br />\n<blockquote>參考資料 菲赴台求醫旅客增加 台灣醫院力推醫療旅遊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2033963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2033963&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=22019483\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2033963</a><br />\n時間：2019-09-10 17:47<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第三點 政府配套<br />\n喺講台灣政府做咗啲咩之前<br />\n我哋先嚟睇下香港政府做咗啲咩嘢<br />\n<blockquote>參考資料 旅發局籌備「香港再出發」計劃 冀吸引外國旅客重臨<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479706-20190909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479706-20190909.htm&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=d92f1228\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479706-20190909.htm&h=b48df320\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479706-20190909.htm</a><br />\n2019-09-09 HKT 22:52<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲嚟講   即係又係賣廣告<br />\n好啦而家我哋睇返台灣<br />\n<blockquote>參考資料 超方便！外國旅客出入境台灣4大措施 上網填登記表「節省審查時間」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190909/1532156.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190909%2F1532156.htm&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=ba49bd7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190909/1532156.htm</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n知道有啲人唔會撳入去睇，我總結少少<br />\n1.上網填寫入國登記表<br />\n2.常客證<br />\n3.「外籍旅客快速查驗閘門」<br />\n4.機場通關禮遇尊榮服務<br />\n<br />\n高下立見啦？<br />\n或者唔係全部措施有效，但係喺呢度最起碼大家可以睇到一樣嘢<br />\n<strong><br />\n一個民選嘅政府，會同你講到好多完整嘅措施，所有嘢都有紋有路<br />\n一個戇鳩嘅政府，會同你講政府有一系列的措施幫助業界，但係講多兩個自己已經講唔到落去</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>旅遊業困局因為示威因為香港唔安全？<br />\nbullshits，因為你政府垃圾，多年來了無作為！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"56ffb6db0008014155859d99912640fd4aed8c69","tid":1559029,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6m2jBL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6m2jBL1.jpg&h=ee9213b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1De952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1De952.jpg&h=92472736&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec92a29bf40dcce04a1e59695248db97b64659f7","tid":1559029,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"就算今日冇示威！旅遊業一樣會差！<br />\n政府亦都唔會幫到旅遊業！<br />\n補貼下賣下廣告！<br />\n之後就同你講我盡曬力㗎啦！<br />\n<blockquote> 參考資料 過度依賴中客 東南亞旅遊業苦吞中國經濟放緩後果<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2907957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2907957&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=7a537ad0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2907957&h=4a5e6388\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2907957</a><br />\n2019-09-06 20:10<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"p